HEADWORD: Cauterization
<hw>Cau`ter*i*za"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>caut⟦egrave⟧risation</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>The act
